The ground went out from under me as I yelled out in anguish. Everything went dark, and the only thing I could hear were the thumps and smashes of my body against the walls.[l][r]
My body hit so many things along the way as we fell. It hurts. It hurts so much.[r]
Much more than one of Chi-chan's punches. It didn't help that my helmet was gone...[l][r]
This is bad.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="0"  method="crossfade"  storage="white.png"  ]
[playse  volume="100"  time="1000"  buf="0"  storage="hit12.ogg"  ]
