[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
But the moment I acknowledged that, my head smashed into something, leaving me dazed. I felt myself going limp and my consciousness beginning to fade...[r]
... but I felt no fear.
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="black.png"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]If I go to sleep forever... if I die...[r]
... then I can be with Chi-chan again...[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[playse  volume="100"  time="1000"  buf="0"  storage="hit03.ogg"  ]
