The fall continues, but there's no pain. Chi-chan, Chi-chan...[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1000"  method="crossfade"  storage="black.png"  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r]I'm coming home.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

